{
  "stem": "5328.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Before the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, well, soon the German occupied, there were no more school for anybody.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because I was still young-- like a kid, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I was-- this was before-- before even the ghetto started-- just a short time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But that was-- even so, I-- I knew German pretty well.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the thing is too, when you don't know a language, so you don't understand, and that's all.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But when you do know a language, and you have to pretend you don't understand it, this is-- this is hard to manage.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because not willingly, you sometimes answer and-- you know, because you know the language.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So that's the way I came to-- to Germany.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had to pretend I didn't know German in Germany.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had to pretend that I didn't know Hebrew and Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But this would come in consideration.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was the hardest part from beginning.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then later, I-- I learned-- like, apparently, I was supposed to learn from them this language.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I-- I spoke such a good German that they didn't-- they couldn't tell that I'm not German.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because being young and working with young-- being in the house with young children and always German-- so I pick up the language very quick.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Which-- now, I don't think-- think even I could-- I understand everything.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But to have to speak, I don't-- I didn't speak since '45 German.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Off and on a little bit, but not-- not constantly.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ukrainian-- Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I didn't have to do anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like, not religious-- because they weren't religious too, the German couple that I lived in.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they-- this-- the job what they-- I mean, I came with the transport from from-- Russia, right?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they-- they're sorted, the people.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
